The paper discusses techniques for improving the performance of constraint solvers, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and programming languages (cs.PL). The use of variable views and derived propagators also involves data structures (cs.DS) and logic (cs.LO). Finally, the paper addresses issues of maintainability and software engineering (cs.SE).
